# Environment Configuration for AI Football Chat

# ===========================================
# OPTION 1: Perplexity AI (Recommended)
# ===========================================
# Uncomment the line below and add your Perplexity API key
# Get your key from: https://www.perplexity.ai/
# PERPLEXITY_API_KEY=your_perplexity_api_key_here

# ===========================================
# OPTION 2: Google Gemini
# ===========================================
# Uncomment the line below and add your Gemini API key
# Get your key from: https://ai.google.dev/
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

